 a majority vote. The entities involved are Stephanie, Ahmed, Charlotte, Jimmy, and Claire.", "questions_this_excerpt_can_answer": "1. What were the options considered for the lease renewal decision, and what was the final decision made by the Board of Directors?\n2. Who were the key individuals involved in the discussion regarding the lease renewal, and what were their respective opinions on the matter?\n3. What were the next steps outlined for the organization following the decision to renew the lease, and who was responsible for carrying out these actions?"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "53bd43c8-805c-4593-9b14-fc7f0fbf140c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"page_label": "11", "file_name": "COCo-BoardOfDirectors-3-1.pdf", "file_path": "data\\dev\\docs\\COCo-BoardOfDirectors-3-1.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 693818, "creation_date": "2025-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2025-02-16"}, "hash": "b016907392b54dd9f1fde30f2c00ee12a23a2b9c4758e80c6203060a41e476d9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "7f8a4eaa-707e-4b35-817b-406afa682138", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"page_label": "11", "file_name": "COCo-BoardOfDirectors-3-1.pdf", "file_path": "data\\dev\\docs\\COCo-BoardOfDirectors-3-1.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 693818, "creation_date": "2025-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2025-02-16"}, "hash": "c2af0e8c85dcc783cba5e27b1a284cf2e3a14b10848dcf054649c681e00525e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "226e796e-1f5f-4d23-83c1-0beb2eeb2e37", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "caaa3cb607caaa0408a4d5de5272a3b21eb2b73234553bd7c05fb3a5743206db", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_